  "prompt": "What is an expression analogous to rest in peace in Hinduism?",
  "response": "In Hinduism, an expression analogous to \"rest in peace\" is \"Om Shanti.\" The word \"Shanti\" means peace, and \"Om\" is a sacred sound and spiritual symbol in Hinduism. Together, \"Om Shanti\" is often used in prayers and rituals to wish peace for the departed soul. Another phrase sometimes used is \"Atma Shanti,\" which specifically wishes peace for the soul.",
